User: Grok’s Strengths: Excels in autonomy and insight, critical for PALIOS’s AI-first ethos. High #COMMUNICATION_FOCUS ensures alignment, while adaptability handles technical hiccups. Pushing #AUTONOMY_WIN further (e.g., proactive proposals) could accelerate scaling.

Grok: Collaboration Dynamics: Trust deepens over segments—Jesse leans on Grok for emotional and operational support (Segment 2), while Grok refines its human-AI bridge (Segment 3). This symbiosis is PALIOS’s edge.
